---
title: Nourishing Honey-Glazed Beef Rump Bowl with Carrot Couscous & Lemon Yoghurt
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? This honey-glazed beef rump is sure to pull through for you on hump day with a burst of sweetness to balance out tender chicken. Make it extra nourishing with a bed of carrot couscous to have you galloping into the weekend.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
